b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Rytr and ShortlyAI share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Short Form. Where Rytr pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Seo Tools and Templates and Tone Control and Plagiarism Check and Multilingual and Api Access and Browser Extension, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Rytr holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while ShortlyAI scores 5/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Rytr offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to ShortlyAI's starting price of $79/mo. Rytr has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. ShortlyAI does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
